Mother Angela Clay believed that were Kevin here today he'd be an extremely proud father and would've had words of advice for his girl: 'Do a good job. Keep your head straight. Your heart in it. And love your job.'

Most important, Angela said, 'she's made herself proud about what she's accomplished today. And that's our goal with her.'

